2. cs.ME (Mechanical Engineering): The paper discusses the dynamic models of the brushes and the design of the brushbots, which are related to mechanical engineering. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper presents motion control algorithms for the brushbots, which is related to systems and control. 
4. cs.ET (Embedded Systems): The brushbots are likely to have embedded systems for their control and operation. 
5. cs.EM (Electromagnetics): The vibration-based locomotion strategy employed by the brushbots involves electromagnetics, which could be relevant to this sub-category.
